Tagline: Honey &amp; Lemon Infused Berliner Weisse.
First brewed: 2016
Description:
Honey &amp; Lemon Blitz sees tart Berliner Weisse character multiplied by lemony acidity; light bready malt and a hint of warming honey hold this back from the brink of palate- destroying sourness.

Food pairing:
[Herb-Crusted Baked Cod, Berry and Cream Meringue, Lemon Drizzle Cake]

